yTime":"2019-11-22T08:17:13.000Z","msg":"我係一個工程師，政府呢幾個月來為左止暴制亂，做左好多野。但建制派呢？呢幾個月來響警察打生打死果陣，日日響屋企飲紅酒食牛扒，一次都冇好似黃屍暴徒咁上過前線支持警察！！<br />\n<br />\n呢幾年我兩家老少廿幾口投建制皆為佢地係做實事，但班靚仔、美國佬依幾個月喺度搞事，建制派完全唔知做過乜，人地組團去外國遊說架，你地拎左我d錢有冇去過美國反遊說？？仲想我投你班含家產？我支持政府做實事，所以一定投白票 / 投對家要你地反省下響立法會選舉前你地應該做乜野！！"},{"pid":"81fe4c612c2e2b5a8c7cbb5b8521a4d9f1c24986","tid":1745394,"uid":158457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T08:17:20.000Z","msg":"中央16連反對美國咁強硬<br />\n民建聯竟然唔跟？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17a8f988da145e36eb4c8ece4dd6bd77230f2c79","tid":1745394,"uid":329551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T08:17:36.000Z","msg":"見到海報貼呢一張上嗰 logo：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i7OtyVf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi7OtyVf.jpg&h=1ca319a4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7e249c1cd399d40dc9713cf403c61f265eb71bc4","tid":1745394,"uid":275243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be721873255451ff2bf9b13897109c58e66be105","tid":1745394,"uid":28114,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:55:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n下面啲留言俾啲愛國藍絲屌到一楝都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T08:22:17.000Z","msg":"話唔定係手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6663a42d29495ce24dbbe4ae383a664cc599cc97","tid":1745394,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T08:25:16.000Z","msg":"驚到瀨屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1438243